<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Episode 20)</i></font>

3
00:00:22,660 --> 00:00:24,491
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini?</font>

4
00:00:25,290 --> 00:00:28,261
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah ini barang-barang Nona Choi?
/ Dia tidak akan bekerja di sini lagi.</font>

5
00:00:28,461 --> 00:00:30,871
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bilang akan menyuruh seseorang
untuk membawakan semua barangnya.</font>

6
00:00:32,001 --> 00:00:35,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia punya 2 lengan dan 2 kaki.
Kenapa tidak bisa membawanya sendiri?</font>

7
00:00:35,200 --> 00:00:37,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa dia menyuruh orang lain?</font>

8
00:00:37,309 --> 00:00:39,718
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu aneh.
/ Apanya?</font>

9
00:00:39,718 --> 00:00:41,278
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkinkah...</font>

10
00:00:42,178 --> 00:00:43,818
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, tidak.</font>

11
00:00:43,818 --> 00:00:45,818
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkinkah apa?</font>

12
00:00:46,218 --> 00:00:47,858
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah menurutmu Nona Choi...</font>

13
00:00:48,519 --> 00:00:51,388
<font color=#FFFF00>...punya <i>leukemia</i>?</font>

14
00:00:53,358 --> 00:00:54,629
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Leukemia</i>?</font>

15
00:00:56,928 --> 00:00:59,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Omong kosong macam apa itu?</font>

16
00:00:59,229 --> 00:01:02,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Lantas, kenapa Dr. Kwak
mencari informasi tentang itu...</font>

17
00:01:02,468 --> 00:01:04,209
<font color=#FFFF00>...setiap kali ada kesempatan?</font>

18
00:01:04,209 --> 00:01:07,679
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimulai sejak hari Nona Choi
pergi ke rumah sakit.</font>

19
00:01:08,509 --> 00:01:11,509
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua ini sangat aneh juga.</font>

20
00:01:11,509 --> 00:01:13,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia memaksa masuk ke asrama kita...,</font>

21
00:01:14,419 --> 00:01:16,819
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan sekarang, dia pindah.</font>

22
00:01:17,218 --> 00:01:19,718
<font color=#FFFF00>Menurutku kau ada benarnya.</font>

23
00:01:29,259 --> 00:01:30,298
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo?</font>

24
00:01:32,069 --> 00:01:33,498
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia menolak melakukan tes?</font>

25
00:01:33,768 --> 00:01:36,869
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku menyuruh dia pindah ke rumahnya
karena khawatir dia terlalu cemas.</i></font>

26
00:01:37,539 --> 00:01:39,138
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah memberiku diagnosismu.</font>

27
00:01:39,238 --> 00:01:41,778
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Itu berdasarkan catatan yang dibawanya.</i></font>

28
00:01:43,649 --> 00:01:46,849
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku perlu menguji dia untuk
mengatur rencana pengobatan.</i></font>

29
00:01:47,378 --> 00:01:50,089
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kecuali itu transplantasi,
kemoterapi adalah taruhan terbaiknya.</i></font>

30
00:01:50,349 --> 00:01:51,949
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan meneleponnya.</font>

31
00:01:57,289 --> 00:02:01,028
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Nomor yang Anda panggil tidak tersedia pada saat ini.</i></font>

32
00:02:06,169 --> 00:02:08,539
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo? Young Eun?</font>

33
00:02:08,638 --> 00:02:10,638
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini Woo Jae.</font>

34
00:02:16,578 --> 00:02:17,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Dr. Song.</font>

35
00:02:22,719 --> 00:02:24,819
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan beritahu kakakku untuk saat ini.</font>

36
00:02:25,689 --> 00:02:27,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa?
/ Tidak apa-apa.</font>

37
00:02:29,189 --> 00:02:30,759
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mau kemana? Ini akhir pekan.</font>

38
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:32,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Bekerja di UGD.</font>

39
00:02:33,699 --> 00:02:35,259
<font color=#FFFF00>Hati hati.</font>

40
00:02:49,578 --> 00:02:51,208
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo.
/ <i>Di mana kau?</i></font>

41
00:02:51,208 --> 00:02:53,749
<font color=#FFFF00>Di asramaku.
/ <i>Haruskah kita makan siang?</i></font>

42
00:02:53,749 --> 00:02:55,018
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ada jadwal di UGD.</font>

43
00:02:55,018 --> 00:02:57,388
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jangan terburu-buru.
Aku mengirimkan mobil untukmu.</i></font>

44
00:03:29,578 --> 00:03:30,719
<font color=#FFFF00>Silahkan.</font>

45
00:03:31,319 --> 00:03:33,618
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus naik perahu juga?</font>

46
00:03:33,618 --> 00:03:36,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini tidak jauh. Hanya 10 menit.</font>

47
00:04:16,729 --> 00:04:17,868
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita turun di sini.</font>

48
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:30,508
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo. Dia baru saja turun.</font>

49
00:05:23,669 --> 00:05:25,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahmu benar-benar terkena kanker?</font>

50
00:05:26,068 --> 00:05:28,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya begitu.
/ Bagaimana kau tahu?</font>

51
00:05:31,868 --> 00:05:35,079
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini diagnosis yang dia dapat di Cina.</font>

52
00:05:36,808 --> 00:05:40,378
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu campuran bahasa Cina dan Inggris,
jadi aku tidak tahu pasti...,</font>

53
00:05:40,579 --> 00:05:41,748
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi bukankah itu kanker...</font>

54
00:05:42,649 --> 00:05:43,988
<font color=#FFFF00>...seperti yang kuduga?</font>

55
00:05:49,159 --> 00:05:50,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu parah?</font>

56
00:05:51,688 --> 00:05:53,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Di mana dia sekarang?</font>

57
00:05:54,128 --> 00:05:56,529
<font color=#FFFF00>Seberapa parah?</font>

58
00:06:12,008 --> 00:06:13,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau terlambat.</font>

59
00:06:14,849 --> 00:06:17,219
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sedang apa disini?</font>

60
00:06:17,318 --> 00:06:19,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau lupa kalau aku anaknya?</font>

61
00:06:21,858 --> 00:06:23,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini pertemuan keluarga.</font>

62
00:06:23,889 --> 00:06:25,988
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tamu kami.</font>

63
00:06:27,798 --> 00:06:28,998
<font color=#FFFF00>Merasa tertekan?</font>

64
00:06:32,198 --> 00:06:35,099
<font color=#FFFF00>Langkah selanjutnya mungkin
membuatmu merasa lebih buruk.</font>

65
00:06:38,469 --> 00:06:39,469
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo.</font>

66
00:06:59,188 --> 00:07:00,399
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

67
00:07:02,128 --> 00:07:05,469
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo.
/ Halo, Pak.</font>

68
00:07:07,198 --> 00:07:09,839
<font color=#FFFF00>Dr. Song, kemarilah.</font>

69
00:07:11,709 --> 00:07:14,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Jae Geol, maafkan kami.
/ Baik.</font>

70
00:07:15,608 --> 00:07:18,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kubilang? Aku bilang
kau akan merasa lebih buruk.</font>

71
00:07:18,678 --> 00:07:19,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Semoga berhasil.</font>

72
00:07:27,919 --> 00:07:29,019
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah kau...</font>

73
00:07:29,959 --> 00:07:31,928
<font color=#FFFF00>...pernah memancing sebelumnya?</font>

74
00:07:32,488 --> 00:07:33,698
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini pertama kalinya.</font>

75
00:07:34,899 --> 00:07:36,198
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus mencobanya.</font>

76
00:07:36,198 --> 00:07:39,099
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini hobi yang sempurna
bagi ahli bedah seperti kita.</font>

77
00:07:40,169 --> 00:07:42,039
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada baiknya untuk keluar zona...</font>

78
00:07:42,039 --> 00:07:44,909
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan tidak memikirkan apa pun sesekali.</font>

79
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:48,508
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau belum bisa melakukan itu, 'kan?</font>

80
00:07:53,318 --> 00:07:56,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu kalau ini dulunya pulau terpencil?</font>

81
00:07:57,019 --> 00:07:59,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, aku tidak tahu.</font>

82
00:08:00,289 --> 00:08:02,818
<font color=#FFFF00>Seorang nelayan menemukannya saat dia...</font>

83
00:08:03,229 --> 00:08:05,358
<font color=#FFFF00>...terdampar di sini karena badai.</font>

84
00:08:06,459 --> 00:08:08,758
<font color=#FFFF00>Baginya, badai itu krisis...,</font>

85
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:10,399
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi dia merawat pulau ini...</font>

86
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:12,729
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan membuatnya seperti sekarang.</font>

87
00:08:12,729 --> 00:08:16,539
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu ternyata menjadi kesempatan besar.</font>

88
00:08:20,308 --> 00:08:21,539
<font color=#FFFF00>Kupikir...</font>

89
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:26,448
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau seperti pulau ini bagi keluargaku.</font>

90
00:08:28,019 --> 00:08:30,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Istriku bertemu badai...</font>

91
00:08:32,188 --> 00:08:35,489
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan kau memberikan tempat
berlindung yang sempurna.</font>

92
00:08:36,318 --> 00:08:39,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, Pak, aku hanya...
/ Sekarang, giliran kami.</font>

93
00:08:41,698 --> 00:08:44,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Seperti nelayan yang merawat pulau ini...,</font>

94
00:08:44,629 --> 00:08:48,438
<font color=#FFFF00>...ini giliran kami untuk menjaga
dan mendukungmu.</font>

95
00:08:52,409 --> 00:08:53,909
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

96
00:08:54,678 --> 00:08:57,208
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo pergi. Makan siang sudah siap.</font>

97
00:08:57,208 --> 00:08:58,279
<font color=#FFFF00>Baik.</font>

98
00:09:11,058 --> 00:09:12,958
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita bisa makan di luar...,</font>

99
00:09:12,958 --> 00:09:15,499
<font color=#FFFF00>....tapi aku ingin menghidangkanmu
makanan rumahan.</font>

100
00:09:15,499 --> 00:09:18,428
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku meminta pemilik untuk meminjamkan dapur.</font>

101
00:09:18,629 --> 00:09:22,039
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami berteman baik.</font>

102
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:23,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

103
00:09:23,869 --> 00:09:25,039
<font color=#FFFF00>Silahkan dimakan.</font>

104
00:09:25,769 --> 00:09:27,708
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harap kau menyukai masakanku.</font>

105
00:09:27,708 --> 00:09:29,978
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu tahu betapa pandainya ibu memasak.</font>

106
00:09:29,978 --> 00:09:31,448
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku seorang intelektual...,</font>

107
00:09:31,448 --> 00:09:33,649
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan intelektual harus rendah hati.</font>

108
00:09:34,149 --> 00:09:35,718
<font color=#FFFF00>Abaikan saja, dan makanlah.</font>

109
00:09:35,718 --> 00:09:38,249
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan kelaparan jika berusaha
meladeni obrolannya.</font>

110
00:09:38,249 --> 00:09:39,958
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa?</font>

111
00:09:53,698 --> 00:09:56,169
<font color=#FFFF00>Hanya berdering?
/ Iya.</font>

112
00:09:56,509 --> 00:09:57,609
<font color=#FFFF00>Coba lagi.</font>

113
00:10:01,509 --> 00:10:03,048
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Heo Jeong Rim)</i></font>

114
00:10:08,879 --> 00:10:11,448
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo?
/ <i>Kau menelepon?</i></font>

115
00:10:13,789 --> 00:10:17,958
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya. Untuk menanyakan
keberadaan Young Eun.</font>

116
00:10:17,958 --> 00:10:19,558
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia sedang bersamaku.</i></font>

117
00:10:20,058 --> 00:10:21,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa bicara dengannya?</font>

118
00:10:22,058 --> 00:10:23,869
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia sedang pergi keluar.</i></font>

119
00:10:25,529 --> 00:10:28,399
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pasti baik-baik saja kalau begitu.</font>

120
00:10:28,568 --> 00:10:32,438
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Iya. Dia terlihat tidak terlalu buruk.</i></font>

121
00:10:32,869 --> 00:10:35,178
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ada apa?</i></font>

122
00:10:35,178 --> 00:10:37,078
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kalian berdua bersama lagi?</i></font>

123
00:10:37,948 --> 00:10:39,478
<font color=#FFFF00>Hubungi aku saat dia pulang.</font>

124
00:10:39,478 --> 00:10:41,978
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika dia tidak mau, kau bisa.</font>

125
00:10:43,188 --> 00:10:44,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih. Dah.</font>

126
00:10:53,698 --> 00:10:55,058
<font color=#FFFF00>Masih berdering?</font>

127
00:10:57,769 --> 00:10:59,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia biasanya mengangkat.</font>

128
00:11:01,039 --> 00:11:03,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kalau dia
pingsan di suatu tempat?</font>

129
00:11:03,968 --> 00:11:05,708
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana jika itu penyebab
dia tidak bisa menjawab?</font>

130
00:11:06,169 --> 00:11:07,708
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu bagaimana?</font>

131
00:11:08,178 --> 00:11:09,678
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan terlalu ketakutan.</font>

132
00:11:13,249 --> 00:11:16,519
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bilang sudah memberinya ponsel, 'kan?</font>

133
00:11:17,489 --> 00:11:19,348
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.
/ Atas nama siapa?</font>

134
00:11:19,448 --> 00:11:21,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku, untuk berjaga-jaga.</font>

135
00:11:24,688 --> 00:11:26,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Lacak saja.</font>

136
00:11:26,129 --> 00:11:28,558
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika atas namamu, kau bisa melacaknya.</font>

137
00:11:28,558 --> 00:11:30,669
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau benar, aku bisa.</font>

138
00:11:30,669 --> 00:11:31,999
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Cari perangkatku)</i></font>

139
00:11:40,539 --> 00:11:43,379
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini...
/ Kau tahu itu di mana?</font>

140
00:11:43,909 --> 00:11:44,978
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

141
00:11:46,818 --> 00:11:48,619
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau punya mobil?</font>

142
00:11:59,558 --> 00:12:02,399
<font color=#FFFF00>Cobalah ini juga.
/ Terima kasih.</font>

143
00:12:05,828 --> 00:12:07,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo, makan lagi.</font>

144
00:12:08,698 --> 00:12:10,968
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau terlalu kurus.</font>

145
00:12:12,539 --> 00:12:13,838
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sedang berusaha.</font>

146
00:12:24,718 --> 00:12:27,289
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf, ini rumah sakit.
/ Angkat saja.</font>

147
00:12:31,958 --> 00:12:33,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Dr. Kang?</font>

148
00:12:36,468 --> 00:12:37,769
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

149
00:12:41,139 --> 00:12:42,269
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa?</font>

150
00:12:43,169 --> 00:12:44,409
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka membutuhkanku.</font>

151
00:12:44,409 --> 00:12:46,338
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menyuruh Dr. Kang
untuk menggantikanmu.</font>

152
00:12:46,978 --> 00:12:49,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak bisa bekerja.
Dia terkena <i>gastroenteritis</i> akut.</font>

153
00:12:49,139 --> 00:12:50,578
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Gejala muntah dan diare)</i></font>

154
00:12:50,578 --> 00:12:53,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah, kau harus pergi.
/ Ya ampun.</font>

155
00:12:53,218 --> 00:12:55,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bahkan belum selesai makan.</font>

156
00:12:55,218 --> 00:12:56,588
<font color=#FFFF00>Antar dia ke sana.</font>

157
00:12:57,289 --> 00:12:59,548
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, agar dia aman.
/ Baik.</font>

158
00:13:04,058 --> 00:13:05,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Selamat tinggal.</font>

159
00:13:42,759 --> 00:13:43,928
<font color=#FFFF00>Masuk.</font>

160
00:13:58,208 --> 00:13:59,478
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasang sabuk pengamanmu.</font>

161
00:14:00,379 --> 00:14:02,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Atau aku akan memasangkannya
jika kau ingin romantis.</font>

162
00:14:37,218 --> 00:14:38,249
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

163
00:14:38,919 --> 00:14:39,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah.</font>

164
00:14:41,588 --> 00:14:43,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Pak. Pak.
/ Ayah.</font>

165
00:14:43,859 --> 00:14:46,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, bangun.Ayah kenapa?</font>

166
00:14:46,129 --> 00:14:48,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia baik-baik saja? Iya?</font>

167
00:14:48,698 --> 00:14:51,399
<font color=#FFFF00>Bangun, Ayah.</font>

168
00:14:57,539 --> 00:14:59,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau suka memancing?</font>

169
00:15:00,039 --> 00:15:01,208
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak tahu.</font>

170
00:15:01,879 --> 00:15:04,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak memancing dengan sembarang orang.</font>

171
00:15:04,609 --> 00:15:06,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia memilih mitra dengan hati-hati.</font>

172
00:15:07,318 --> 00:15:09,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kriterianya?</font>

173
00:15:09,119 --> 00:15:11,688
<font color=#FFFF00>Keluarga atau sahabat.</font>

174
00:15:11,789 --> 00:15:13,218
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak termasuk keduanya.</font>

175
00:15:13,218 --> 00:15:14,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Menurutku kau termasuk keduanya.</font>

176
00:15:15,818 --> 00:15:17,989
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya ayahku ingin kau...</font>

177
00:15:17,989 --> 00:15:20,428
<font color=#FFFF00>...menjadi keluarga dan sahabatnya.</font>

178
00:15:22,198 --> 00:15:23,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah kita menikah?</font>

179
00:15:24,828 --> 00:15:26,769
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami butuh seseorang
untuk mewarisi rumah sakit.</font>

180
00:15:26,769 --> 00:15:28,468
<font color=#FFFF00>Bidangku tidak cocok.</font>

181
00:15:28,539 --> 00:15:31,009
<font color=#FFFF00>Menurutku dia ingin
memberikannya untukmu.</font>

182
00:15:32,509 --> 00:15:33,938
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebagai menantunya.</font>

183
00:15:35,509 --> 00:15:37,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tertarik?</font>

184
00:15:37,649 --> 00:15:38,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu.</font>

185
00:15:39,409 --> 00:15:41,149
